==English==
===Noun===
'''potluck'''
# A [[meal]], especially one [[offer|offered]] to a [[guest]], consisting of whatever is [[available]].
#: ''Here's a good potluck of [[bean|beans]] and [[stew]].''
# A meal consisting of whatever guests have brought.
# [[whatever|Whatever]] is available in a particular situation.
# A [[gathering]] of people bringing foods from different parts of the world.
#: ''The [[Arabic]] [[cuisine]] at the potluck was [[delicious]].''

